Titolo: Aoi Shiro

Anno: 2008

Descrizione: Aoi Shiro (アオイシロ, 'Blue Castle') is an adventure game by Japanese developer and publisher Success Corporation, released for the PlayStation 2 in Japan on April 5, 2008, and was later ported to Microsoft Windows with extra content. A reduced price "popular edition," included in the SuperLite 2000 Series, was released on April 28, 2009.